description: Rice Burner is bringing the “mmm mmm mmm!!!” to Memphis with this delicious Japanese fusion cuisine, with just the right touch of Southern hospitality.Their menu features their famous Hibachi Burner: a delicious dish of fried rice, onions, and zucchini, with your choice of meat (including teriyaki chicken, shrimp, steak, etc..) and sauce. With all this more, of course, it’s no wonder all the locals yearn for the fantastic food from Rice Burner.
name: Rice Burner
